OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChampions League: Police   
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fchief admits security      
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Ffailure                    
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The head of policing at the Champions  
OL,6, League final in Paris has apologised   
OL,7, for using tear gas on Liverpool fans   
OL,8, but said he had no alternative.        
OL,10,FDidier Lallement admitted the security 
OL,11,Foperation was "obviously a failure".   
OL,13,FBut he defended the tactics he used as 
OL,14,Fchaotic scenes unfolded outside the    
OL,15,FStade de France last month, insisting  
OL,16,Fhis "red line" was to save lives.      
OL,18,FFrench authorities blamed late arrivals
OL,19,Fand fake tickets for overcrowding and  
OL,20,Fchaotic scenes before the match.       
